data.description: Come check out this adorable brick ranch in a desirable part of Norfolk! Close to shopping, the airport, interstate, and military bases. This house has well maintained original hardwood floors, new water heater 2021, new electrical outlets 2019, kitchen and bathroom plumbing replaced 2019. Large fenced in yard ready for entertaining, pets, kids, gardening, you name it! All appliances including washer and dryer do convey.
